{"word":"ὀαρίζω","slug":"ὀαρίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὀαρίζω</b></el> <el>(ὀᾰρίζω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ὄαρος'><el>ὄαρος</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>used in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> and <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a>\n<p/><i>to converse</i> or <i>chat with</i> one, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <el>ὀαριζέμεναι</el> (epic <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a>) <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/>"}]}